    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You carve glowing runes into your skin, creating a dormant seal that can be activated as an instant action to grant you a +2 competence bonus to a single weapon damage roll or a +4 competence bonus to a single Strength-based check. The seal can be activated only if it's bonus would be used immediately, before the result of the roll is known, and disappears afterwards. You take 2 damage every time you attempt to perform this technique. Your body cannot carry more than one Potency seal.</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Empower:</b> Spend double the Chakra and double the damage dealt to you to double the bonuses granted. Doing so makes you unable to use this technique or Ketsuyoujutsu: Kaisoku for 24 hours.</p>\n\n",
